33:36.680 --> 33:37.750
They make them worse.

33:37.800 --> 33:39.040
Stell?

33:39.100 --> 33:40.465
You okay?

33:40.510 --> 33:44.060
I don't think
I can do this, Wes.

33:45.640 --> 33:48.974
I'm not ready
to have a baby.

33:56.490 --> 33:58.401
