33:58.450 --> 34:02.193
You said that
you wanted our little girl.

34:02.240 --> 34:03.401
What changed?

34:06.080 --> 34:09.072
I just got this clean slate,
you know?

34:10.710 --> 34:14.089
And I've been trying to figure
out who I'm supposed to be.

34:14.130 --> 34:16.371
And I realize
that every choice,

34:16.429 --> 34:18.580
every single decision
I've ever made

34:18.639 --> 34:21.849
has been based
on me being sick.

34:21.889 --> 34:23.927
Birthdays on hold.
Christmas in July.

34:23.969 --> 34:25.347
Thanksgiving on Easter.

34:25.389 --> 34:27.518
And it's not just because
it's a better holiday.

34:27.560 --> 34:30.018
It's because nobody thought

34:30.060 --> 34:32.266
that I would make it
to November.

34:34.070 --> 34:35.481
Even you and I got married

34:35.530 --> 34:38.818
because we thought
we had no time.

